sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Layout
    participant useScrollPosition
    participant AppBar
    participant HomePage
    participant useHashNavigation
    participant AnimatedCard
    participant LazyImage
    participant ImageUploader
    participant UploadAPI
    participant RichTextEditor
    participant AdminSettings

    Note over User,Layout: 场景1: 导航栏滚动效果
    User->>Layout: 访问首页
    Layout->>useScrollPosition: 初始化hook
    useScrollPosition-->>Layout: scrollY=0 (透明AppBar)
    User->>Layout: 向下滚动
    Layout->>useScrollPosition: 监听scroll
    useScrollPosition-->>Layout: scrollY>50 (纯色AppBar)
    Layout->>AppBar: bgcolor=#0F2B47, boxShadow=2

    Note over User,HomePage: 场景2: 锚点导航
    User->>HomePage: 点击导航链接#products-section
    HomePage->>useHashNavigation: navigateToAnchor("products-section")
    useHashNavigation->>useHashNavigation: 更新URL hash
    useHashNavigation->>useHashNavigation: scrollIntoView({behavior:"smooth"})

    Note over User,AnimatedCard: 场景3: 卡片hover动效
    User->>AnimatedCard: 鼠标hover
    AnimatedCard->>AnimatedCard: scale=1.01 + borderColor=primary.main
    AnimatedCard-->>User: 视觉反馈

    Note over User,ImageUploader: 场景4: 后台图片上传
    User->>ImageUploader: 选择图片
    ImageUploader->>UploadAPI: POST /upload/image
    UploadAPI-->>ImageUploader: {url, thumbnailUrl}
    ImageUploader-->>User: 显示预览

    Note over User,RichTextEditor: 场景5: 富文本编辑
    User->>RichTextEditor: 编辑产品描述
    RichTextEditor-->>AdminProducts: onChange(htmlString)
    AdminProducts->>AdminProducts: 保存到数据库
